Packed layout record Word has value: u16.

To layout write into view, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0.
Let window be view of bytes from 1 for 2.
Let word be Word with value be 258.
Write word into window at 0.
Give (bytes at 1 as i32) plus ((bytes at 2 as i32) times 10).

To main, giving i32.
Give layout write into view.
